{"tid":303161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金鐘「雜總過主」塗鴉不敵高壓水槍","createTime":"2017-06-30T03:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T09:49:01.000Z","uid":39464,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"121f31dc2e949188477b675a1752dd9d671ce3a0","tid":303161,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170630/large/1498789763_6e60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170630%2Flarge%2F1498789763_6e60.jpg&h=69e3863c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170630/large/1498789765_5076.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170630%2Flarge%2F1498789765_5076.jpg&h=decd6f28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然港府高調慶祝香港回歸20年，惟民心尚未回歸。有人趁國家主席習近平訪港，在曾發生佔領行動的金鐘夏愨道，以黃色噴漆寫上「港人自主，雜種過主」的抗議字句，當局發現後早上急急派人到場清洗。<br />\n<br />\n現場是金鐘海富中心和政府總部之間一段夏愨道，有人昨晚發現西行線靠近巴士站的馬路上，被人用黃色噴漆寫上約一米乘半米的「港人自主，雜種過主」標語，但並無下款，暫未知出自誰人手筆。<br />\n<br />\n當局發現「倒習」標語後，早上約9點半派清潔工人到場清洗，工人先嘗試用掃帚洗擦，但發現無法將標語洗掉，唯有改用高壓水槍集中噴洗，再加上掃帚出力洗擦，才慢慢將字句洗去，但相信早有不少市民已看到該標語。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56895239&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170630\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56895239%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170630&d=jdE0CXUA4ZDiSTzF1B2RBr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=a00da92d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56895239%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170630&h=5e184720\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56895239&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170630</a>"},{"pid":"5618651623e80dd11f938b2006b0ef56fc265471","tid":303161,"uid":3028,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:06:10.000Z","msg":"但並無下款，暫未知出自誰人手筆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d816ebd990fb4bd07a0a51b95133054f65a5e245","tid":303161,"uid":92301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8944db53938f71f0eee6c0145e5d05aedff6de1","tid":303161,"uid":62864,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:07:23.000Z","msg":"蘋果反了，有邊個講過習總喺雜種先?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711f35a55455fa7b7ac729a37cfe04b3f04e7a78","tid":303161,"uid":44562,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:09:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蘋果反了，有邊個講過習總喺雜種先?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n敵唔過蘋果 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e963b0875f9d431a89e51eaa98005eba15aa7cc","tid":303161,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:09:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蘋果反了，有邊個講過習總喺雜種先?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af01a0d2e215a13ae995d9ada90e390044908f49","tid":303161,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:15:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"160bff962192329be3979bf98f9dfba2030fbe59","tid":303161,"uid":67353,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:21:45.000Z","msg":"下次下款寫689就真係689咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}